title: Combat Cats v1.0.96
description:
The catnip has been stolen, can you bring peace and harmony back to Kitty Island? --- Puzzle, gem matching, RPG, adventure for all ages!

Match bricks/gems to set off devastating combos while fighting off enemies, as you collect coins and catnip to upgrade and advance through the game.
Combat Cats is unlike any other brick matching game!

- Match bricks in any pattern you want. 
- Earn extra points and do more damage for bigger combos.
- Fire off nuclear weapons!
- Pop pesky water bubbles that block your game board.
- Upgrade stats, weapons, aircraft!
- Unlock achievements!
